---
BasedOnStyle: Google
ColumnLimit: 100
DerivePointerAlignment: false
IncludeBlocks: Preserve
LineEnding: LF
# Treat clang-tidy NOLINT* comments as pragmas so clang-format does not wrap
# them; wrapping splits the rationale onto a new line and the NOLINTNEXTLINE
# stops applying to the intended source line.
CommentPragmas: '^ ?(NOLINT(NEXTLINE|BEGIN|END)?|clang-format|MARK|TODO|FIXME)'
...
